<l>nerunaṟṟuc ceṉṟāreṅ kātalar yāmu</l>
<l> meḻunāḷē mēṉi pacantu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It was but yesterday my lover departed (from me) and it is seven days since my complexion turned sallow.</l>
